  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图来对比两个指标命名规范。一个是下划线格式的 mq_queue_published_total，另一个是点分格式的 mq.queue.published_total。我想用从左到右的布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "mq_queue_published_total",
        "mq.queue.published_total",
        "LR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，左右布局。那这两个指标节点之间需要连线吗？还是保持独立？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "metric0",
        "metric1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要连一条线，表示它们是同一指标的不同命名形式。另外节点标签我想显示 name 属性，比如 name: \"mq_queue_published_total\" 这种格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "metric0",
        "metric1",
        "name attribute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把两个节点建出来，左边是 metric0，右边是 metric1，都加上 name 标签，然后用实线连起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "metric0",
        "metric1",
        "edge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "节点和连线都对。不过标签文字有点长，能不能把字体调小一点？比如 9 像素？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "classDef",
        "font-size"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "可以，我加一个 classDef small 定义，设置 font-size: 9px，然后应用到这两个指标节点上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "classDef small",
        "metric0",
        "metric1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "看起来没问题了。等等，右边那个节点的 name 值，我确认一下应该是 mq.queue.published_total 带点号的，不是下划线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "metric1",
        "mq.queue.published_total"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下 metric1 的 name 值，把下划线改成点分格式：name: \"mq.queue.published_total\"。现在两个节点格式统一了，左边下划线，右边点分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "metric1",
        "mq.queue.published_total"
      ],
